**Prompt**

This exercise is an introduction to PHP programming. Below is a program written with PHP. Your task is to rewrite the
program. The next chapter will teach you how the program works and what it actually does.

<?php

    echo "This is the first program.";

    echo "PHP, here we go!";

?>

**Solution**

<?php

    echo "This is the first program.PHP, here we go!";

?>
